                    <!-- Technical Note: Allow users to set the default local VA facility telephone number in the space provided. Technical Note: Upon completion of this documentation template, with a positive screen for suicide risk, activate the Order Set: Mental Health - Positive Suicide Risk Screening KNART.  End Documentation Template –Suicide Risk Assessment. -->
                </subElements>
            </actionGroup>
        </subElements>
    </actionGroup>
